</code></pre> <ul> <li>flexbox, padding : <code>flex</code>, <code>shrink-0</code>, <code>p-6</code></li> <li>max-width, margin : <code>max-w-sm</code>, <code>mx-auto</code></li> <li>background-color, border radius, box-shadow : <code>bg-white</code>, <code>rounded-xl</code>, <code>shadow-lg</code></li> <li>width, height : <code>w-12</code>, <code>h-12</code></li> <li>space-between : <code>space-x-4</code></li> <li>font-size, text color, font-weight : <code>text-xl</code>, <code>text-black</code>, <code>font-medium</code></li> </ul> <p>Tailwind CSS의 이점?</p> <ul> <li>You aren’t wasting energy inventing class names</li> <li>Your CSS stops growing</li> <li>Making changes feels safer</li> </ul>

반응형 웹 디자인 구축 Breakpoint prefix Minimum width sm 640px md 768px lg 1024px xl 1280px 2xl 1536px Example<pre><code>&lt;div class="max-w-md mx-auto bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden md:max-w-2xl"&gt;
  &lt;div class="md:flex"&gt;
    &lt;div class="md:shrink-0"&gt;
